info.name: Mango Dahi Bhalla
info.description:
Serves 1 | The Mango Edit: Our curated collection of summer's favorite fruit.

Item Includes:

- Mango curd each of 180gm
- Topped with Tamarind chutney, and 
- Garnished with beetroot,Anardana,Coriander leaf(Dhania) & ginger.

~ A delightful summer snack, Mango Dahi Bhalla features soft lentil dumplings soaked in creamy yogurt and topped with sweet mango pulp, tangy chutneys, and spices for a refreshing treat.

*Garnished with Sev & Pomegranate – A delightful crunch & a fruity burst!

~ A fusion of flavors, Mango Bhalla Papdi combines crispy papdi with soft Bhalla's and a generous topping of sweet mango pulp, yogurt, and spices, creating a delightful summer appetizer.

info.name: Mango Bhel Puri

info.name: Chena Murki
info.description: A traditional Indian sweet made by simmering cubes of fresh paneer (chhena) in sugar syrup until they become crystallized and coated with a glossy, sweet glaze. A delightful and crunchy sweet treat.

info.name: Plain Sandesh
info.description: A popular Bengali sweet made from fresh chhena (paneer or cottage cheese), typically flavored with cardamom and sweetened with sugar, offering a simple and delightful dessert.Item includes 22-24 pieces of Plain Sandesh approximately in 1KG box.

info.name: Kesar Sandesh
info.description: A popular Bengali sweet made from fresh chhena (paneer or cottage cheese) and flavored with saffron (kesar), offering a creamy and aromatic dessert.

info.name: Mini Sandesh
info.description: Soft and spongy Bengali sweets made from chenna, lightly sweetened for a melt-in-your-mouth experience.

info.name: Raskadam
info.description: A delightful Indian sweet made by deep-frying small, round dumplings of condensed milk, khoya (milk solids), and sugar until they turn golden brown. These dumplings are then soaked in sugar syrup, creating a sweet and syrupy treat with a rich, creamy center.Item Includes 1 piece of Raskadam.

info.name: Kacha Gola Sandesh
info.description: A traditional Bengali delicacy crafted from fresh chenna, offering a rich and crumbly texture.

info.name: Pakiza
info.description: A Heavenly Dessert to Satisfy Your Sweet Cravings. This sweet is Soft, Syrup-Soaked Pastry Layers Filled with Creamy Delights. Item Includes 1 piece of Pakiza.

info.name: Rasmalai
info.description: Soft, spongy cheese patties soaked in fragrant saffron-flavored milk, topped with pistachios and almonds. A rich, traditional Indian dessert perfect for festive celebrations.

info.name: Coconut Burfi
info.description: Coconut barfi, is a popular and delicious Indian sweet made from grated coconut, sugar, and milk.Item Includes 15-16 piecesapproximate in 1 KG box.

info.name: Chaka Chak
info.description: Syrup-soaked sweet dumplings.

info.name: Coconut Kesariya Burfi
info.description: A rich and flavorful Indian sweet made from grated coconut, sugar, and a touch of saffron, resulting in a delightful, golden-hued dessert.Item includes 28-30 pieces of Coconut Kesariya Burfi in 1 KG box.

info.name: Sandesh Kacha Gola
info.description: A unique Indian dessert where sandesh (a sweet made from paneer or chhena) is molded into small, spherical shapes, resembling ice cream scoops, creating a delightful and creamy sweet treat.

info.name: Kheer Mohan
info.description: A traditional Bengali sweet, Kheer Mohan features soft and spongy chhena (paneer) balls soaked in sweet, saffron-infused milk, creating a creamy and delightful dessert.

info.name: Laddu Coconut Orange
info.description: A unique twist to the classic coconut laddu, infused with a hint of orange flavor.

info.name: Malai Rabri Cup
info.description: A delightful Indian dessert, featuring condensed milk and cream (malai) slow-cooked into a thick, creamy rabri, often served in cups for a creamy and indulgent treat.Item includes 1 piece of Malai Rabri Cup.

info.name: Malai Rasgulla (1pcs.)
info.description: Malai Rasgulla is a soft and spongy dessert made from fresh paneer soaked in sweet, rich, and flavorful sugar syrup. This item includes 1 Piece of Malai Rasgulla.

info.name: Shahi Rasmalai
info.description: A royal and luxurious variation of the traditional rasmalai. It's made by soaking flattened chhena (paneer) discs in saffron-infused, sweetened milk, often garnished with silver leaf and chopped nuts.Item Includes-1 Piece of Rasmalai.

info.name: Malai Roll
info.description: A delectable Indian dessert made by rolling creamy, sweetened condensed milk into cylindrical shapes, often garnished with pistachios or almonds. A delightful and rich sweet treat.This item includes 1 piece of Malai Roll.

info.name: Malai Chap
info.description: A delicious Indian dessert made from condensed milk and flavored with cardamom, then shaped into small, soft, and creamy bites. A delightful sweet treat.Item Includes 1 piece of Malai Chaap.

info.name: Cham Cham
info.description: A popular Indian sweet made from fresh paneer (chhena), cooked in sugar syrup and often flavored with cardamom or rose water. These soft, spongy, and syrup-soaked sweets are often garnished with grated coconut or chopped nuts.This item includes approximately 1 piece of Cham Cham.

info.name: Chena Toast
info.description: A savory Indian snack made by spicing up paneer (cottage cheese) with herbs and spices, spreading it on bread slices, and toasting them until crispy and golden brown. A flavorful and crunchy treat.This Item includes 1 piece of Chena Toast.

info.name: Mohan Bhog

These laddus are often made using gram flour, ghee, sugar, and flavored with cardamom or other spices, resulting in a unique and delectable taste.There are approximately 24 to 28 pieces of laddu bikaneri in each 1KG box.

info.name: Mathura Peda
info.description: A famous sweet from the city of Mathura in India, it's a delectable milk-based sweet made from condensed milk, khoya (milk solids), and flavored with cardamom.

info.name: Khoya Chocolate Burfi

info.name: Khoya Kesar Burfi

info.name: Khoya Fruit Cake
info.description: A sweet and fruity Indian dessert made from khoya (milk solids) mixed with dried fruits and nuts, shaped into a cake-like form for a rich and flavorful treat.

info.name: Dry Kesar Petha 400g
info.description: Bikano Kesar Petha is a regal confectionery delight that epitomizes the richness of Indian sweets. Crafted from tender ash gourd (petha) pieces, soaked in a luxurious saffron-infused syrup, each bite offers a burst of sweetness and aromatic saffron flavor. This royal delicacy is beloved for its soft texture and exquisite taste, making it a cherished treat during festive celebrations and special occasions, serving as a symbol of opulence and tradition.
